    "body" : "<p>If your string contains numbers only, you can make it an integer and then do padding:</p>\n\n<pre><code>String.format(\"%010d\", Integer.parseInt(mystring));\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>If not <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/4421400/how-to-get-0-padded-binary-representation-of-an-integer-in-java\">I would like to know how it can be done</a>.</p>\n"
