      "body" : "Just as a reminder... <code>String</code> is immutable (see <i><a href=\"http://stackoverflow.com/q/8798403/1064325\">String is immutable. What exactly is the meaning?</a></i>), so <code>StringUtils.leftPad(variable, 10, &quot;0&quot;);</code> won&#39;t change the <code>variable</code>&#39;s value. You&#39;d need to assign the result to it, like this: <code>variable = StringUtils.leftPad(variable, 10, &quot;0&quot;);</code>."
