    "body" : "<p>If you need performance and know the maximum size of the string use this:</p>\n\n<pre><code>String zeroPad = \"0000000000000000\";\nString str0 = zeroPad.substring(str.length()) + str;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Be aware of the maximum string size. If it is bigger then the StringBuffer size, you'll get a <code>java.lang.StringIndexOutOfBoundsException</code>.</p>\n"
